sql:
SELECT DISTINCT cookie_provider 
FROM cookies 
WHERE technical_requirement = 1 AND first_party = 0;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT user_id)
FROM cookie_consent
WHERE consent_status IN (0, 1);

SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM cookie_consent 
WHERE consent_status = 1;

SELECT setting_value
FROM cookie_settings
WHERE setting_name = 'cookie_duration';

SELECT role_name, permissions
FROM roles
ORDER BY role_name;

SELECT total_views, total_consent_given, views_last_updated, consent_last_updated
FROM analytics
WHERE cookie_id = 0;

external_knowledge:
Essential and practical cookies refer to 'Necessary' and 'Functional' cookie types;
Renowned providers are considered to be 'DAAD' and 'Google LLC';
Approved means the consent status is given (1);
Initial months of last year points to the consent date being between January 1, 2023, and February 1, 2023.

sql:
SELECT cookies.cookie_name, analytics.total_views
FROM cookies
INNER JOIN analytics ON cookies.cookie_id = analytics.cookie_id;

SELECT COUNT(cookie_id) AS total_consented_cookies
FROM cookie_consent
WHERE user_id = 1 AND consent_status = 1;
